  "texts": [
    "From this meticulous screening and review process, 22 studies were initially selected for inclusion in the review.",
    "In response to feedback and the identified need for broader coverage, nine additional studies were subsequently included, bringing the total number of studies reviewed to 31.",
    "These studies were chosen based on their relevance and potential to provide valuable insights into the field.",
    "After carefully analyzing the research articles, we selected three patients as an example of the characteristics of high-quality TPD proposed by (Borko et al. 2010; Huang et al. 2022).",
    "This selection highlights the stringent criteria and methodological rigor underpinning the systematic review process, ensuring the findings are reliable and relevant to the research question."
  ],
